**This error occurred.**

- The solution is to press Alt+F3 on error screen.
- Now in the ubuntu terminal, enter 'ip a', we will look for any interface such as ens32, ens33 etc. along with an IP (192.168….).
- We will try pinging to 8.8.8.8 to ensure stable network connection.
- We will also try pinging to archive.ubuntu.com. This will test DNS.
